creator: SmootyDevDes
descriptionHtml:
Commitments
- Constant replenishment of icons
- Support for popular launchers
- Grouping icons, there is a New tab to view new icons
- Unique 192x192 high resolution icons
- Handmade icons
- Selected high definition wallpapers
- Modern toolbar where you can browse and search for icons
- Submitting a request to create a recovery
- Light / Dark theme app

Support:
ABC, Action, ADW, Apex, Atom, Aviate, BlackBerry, CM, CPL, Evie, Flick, GO EX, Holo, Holo HD, Lawnchair, LG Home, Lucid, M, Microsoft, Mini, Next, Niagara, Nougat, Poco , Posidon, Smart, Solo, Square, V, ZenUi, Zero

You can contact us SmootyDevDes@gmail.com
Thanks to you! We will be able to replenish the application with a variety of colorful icons and splash screens. We are not professionals in development, this is our hobby. This project is not for the money, so it is free and has no ads. Of course, you can support us with a donation, but this is your business!
descriptionShort: Check out the ever-growing Icon Pack with gorgeous wallpapers, no ads.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We continue to replenish our pack with icons, at the moment we take ideas from the top GPlay, but you can also give us an idea by making a request!
Fixed the binding on some launchers.
Thank you for being with us!
